some of Los Angeles' oldest cathedrals and churches from noon to 5 p.m. March 
13. Buddhist temples in Little Tokyo and Koreatown will be included. The 
"Sacred Structures" tour is sponsored by the Department of Continuing Education 
of the University of Judaism. Participants will discuss Jewish-Christian 
relations with the director of ecumenical affairs for the Roman Catholic 
Archdiocese of Los Angeles. For registration information, call (310) 476-9777, 
Ext. 246. 
</P>
