<HEADLINE>
<P>
BURBANK AIRPORT PROVED INVALUABLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I hope the Los Angeles Times and our fellow survivors in the 6.8 quake in 
the San Fernando Valley will join me in thanking Burbank Airport for being 
there, and for making possible the President's visit to the Valley.It was there 
when we needed help. 
</P>
<P>
 The Burbank Airport's value to the Valley in emergency situations is 
unquestioned. The airport was "shaken" but it kept on "bakin'," to the benefit 
of us all. 
</P>
<P>
 Thank you Burbank Airport, for being a friend indeed. 
</P>
<P>
 R. C. CZAPIEWSKI 
</P>
<P>
 North Hollywood 
</P>
