NBC THURSDAY-NIGHT LINEUP TO RETURN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 To nobody's surprise, NBC said it will bring its popular Thursday-night 
comedies back next season. "Mad About You," "Wings," "Seinfeld" and "Frasier" 
were given full-season orders for 1994-95. 
</P>
