</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Trying to stave off streaking Stanford, Pacific 10 Conference leader USC will 
play UCLA tonight at 7 in a women's basketball game at Pauley Pavilion. 
</P>
<P>
 Coach Cheryl Miller's Trojans, 20-3 overall and 13-2 in the conference, have 
three games left and are being hotly pursued by the Cardinal (19-5, 12-3) and 
