<P>
 COACH: Brian Flatten 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 42-36 04,20,05,07,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Jeff 
DePippo Sr. C R-R Scott Foley Sr. P R-R Ryan Johansen Jr. Util. R-R Eric 
Martinez Jr. OF R-R Erik Maurer Sr. P-INF R-R 04,18,05,07,05 TOP RETURNERS YR. 
POS. B-T Ramon Alliman Sr. OF R-R Nick Stollenwerk Sr. DH-OF R-R 04,16,05,06,05 
