<P>
 COACH: Dave Demarest 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 368-137 04,20,05,08,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Sean 
Carlson Sr. 1B L-R Anibal De La Cruz Sr. OF R-R Joe Linck Sr. C L-R C.J. 
