RETURNEES YR POS Mike Ferguson Sr. P-SS Dusty Cook Jr. RHP David Helman Sr. OF 
Mike Andrisano Sr. OF Nick Andrisano Sr. C Brian Dueppan Sr. P * 03,16,05,07 
